name: IT201 Sprint 4 (kylepinon29)
description: Mom wants you to collect 6 strawberries in the forest in order to make her dessert for dinner! Collect all the 6 strawberries to eat dinner, Use WASD keys to move the player around and Spacebar to jump. You can also right-click to create a cube to find strawberries that are hard to reach even while jumping.
